snippet.title: Actors Who Left With Permanent Damage After A Role | Movies and Popcorn
snippet.description:
Actors aren’t the characters they play in shows. They’re real human beings with feelings. Stars who put everything they had to roles that demanded intense emotional and/or physical investment, ended up permanently damaged by their dedication to the film.
